  "detailed_description": "One Night In The House is a first-person game with an emphasis on plot.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs an Onith employee, you must fulfill the request of your friend who made a fatal mistake.<br />\r\nBut trying to fulfill this request leads you to even greater problems.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the first episode, you have to find a way out of the situation in which you find yourself because of your friend.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse the phone of the main character to communicate in the messenger to search for answers.<br />\r\nUse the smartphone app of the protagonist \"ARNote\" to study notes scattered around the world to help you find a way out.",
  "about_the_game": "One Night In The House is a first-person game with an emphasis on plot.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs an Onith employee, you must fulfill the request of your friend who made a fatal mistake.<br />\r\nBut trying to fulfill this request leads you to even greater problems.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the first episode, you have to find a way out of the situation in which you find yourself because of your friend.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse the phone of the main character to communicate in the messenger to search for answers.<br />\r\nUse the smartphone app of the protagonist \"ARNote\" to study notes scattered around the world to help you find a way out.",
